title: Michael Burry Defends His Nvidia Criticism As Company Pushes Back
description: Michael Burry is standing by his criticism of Nvidia Corp. even after a report said the leading artificial intelligence company pushed back on his analysis. Burry, who became famous for his bets against the housing market during the 2008 financial crisis, last week in a post on X called out the company for its stock-based compensation dilution and stock buybacks. Nvidia responded by sending a memo to Wall Street analysts over the weekend to address such claims, according to a Barron’s report.
